        "subject": "LU-15895 o2iblnd: check if noop is needed on immediate msg rx",
        "message": "LU-15895 o2iblnd: check if noop is needed on immediate msg rx\n\nIf receiving a lot of immediate messages without having to\nsend anything back, peer credits may be returned too late.\n\nTo prevent the peer from running out of credits in this case,\nadd the check whether noop is needed to immediate rx handling.\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial  testlist=sanity-lnet\nSigned-off-by: Serguei Smirnov <ssmirnov@whamcloud.com>\nChange-Id: I1a488ef99d33166aa0ca489662f70560867dc447\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
